        Find loadable mods in this enumerator's domain.

      • register

        public void register(ModularEnumerator enumerator,
                     java.lang.String profile)
        Description copied from interface: EnumeratorModule
        Register loadable mods discovered in this enumerator's domain during the call to EnumeratorModule.enumerate(com.mumfrey.liteloader.interfaces.ModularEnumerator, java.lang.String), the enumerator module should call back against the enumerator itself to register containers it discovers using the registerModContainer() and registerTweakContainer() callbacks.

        This method is called during loader PREINIT phase so do not use any game classes here!
